l projects that are expected to\nmake significant impact in this growing, exciting field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Oct 2016 16:44:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Sep 2018 14:55:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-18"}
