 the\nQGPs indicates towards small covering factor and patchy distribution of cold\ngas clouds around low-z galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Oct 2016 20:00:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-14"}
