ampaign participation. Users' personal interests, approximated by\nFacebook user like activity, turned out to be the best indicator of campaign\nparticipation. Our results demonstrated that a predictive model which leverages\nthe aforementioned features accurately identifies campaign participants\n(AUC=0.76).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Oct 2016 21:10:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-19"}
