 well. Their\nsignatures might be the most promising electromagnetic counterparts for\ngravitational waves merger's signals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Oct 2016 21:17:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-04"}
