 'one SEP event with multiple spacecraft'. A functional relation\nI_{max}(r)=kr^{-1.7} quantifying the radial dependence of SEP peak intensities\nis obtained and utilized in the analysis of physical mechanism. The\nrelationship between our results and those of Dresing et al. is also discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2016 09:04:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-19"}
